{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-045__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-045", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-045__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "chapter", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 45", "sort_key": "045.000", "text_original": "大成若缺，其用不弊。\n\n大盈若沖，其用不窮。\n\n大直若屈，\n\n大巧若拙，\n\n大辯若訥。\n\n躁勝寒，靜勝熱。清靜為天下正。", "text_normalized": "大成若缺，其用不弊。\n\n大盈若沖，其用不窮。\n\n大直若屈，\n\n大巧若拙，\n\n大辯若訥。\n\n躁勝寒，靜勝熱。清靜為天下正。", "notes": ""}
